data.title: Picture post card of George Martin Foster and Ida Florence Williams-Foster, "Ma and Pa Foster"; about 1914.
data.meta_description: George Martin Foster and Ida Florence Williams-Foster were my great grand parents and were called Ma and Pa Foster.  They're buried in the Bethel Cemetery in Anderson County, Tennessee.  George Martin Foster was born on December 20, 1870 and passed away on April 9, 1958.  Ida Florence Williams-Foster was born on March 5, 1874 and passed away on September 25, 1965.
